12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 34 O.S. 2021, Section 8, as
14 amended by Section 1, Chapter 364, O.S.L. 2024 (34 O.S. Supp. 2024,
15 Section 8) is amended to read as follows:
16 Section 8. A. When a citizen or citizens desire to circulate a
17 petition initiating a proposition of any nature, whether to become a
18 statute law or an amendment to the Constitution, or for the purpose
19 of invoking a referendum upon legislative enactments, such citizen
20 or citizens shall, when such petition is prepared, and before the
21 same is circulated or signed by electors, file a true and exact copy
22 of same in the office of the Secretary of State and shall at the
23 same time file a separate ballot title, which shall not be part of
24 or printed on the petition.
